an class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints the tuple b</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints the number 1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints the number 2</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints (3,4,5)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints the numbers 1,2,3,4,5</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => prints the numbers 9,8,7,6,5</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"Args and Kwargs in Python","date":"November 02, 2020","spoiler":"Best way to pass variables across functions.","cta":null},"fields":{"slug":"/args-and-kwargs/","langKey":"en"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/args-and-kwargs/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/the-with-statement/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"the-with-statement","maybeAbsoluteLinks":[]},"frontmatter":{"title":"The With Statement in Python"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/array-data-structures/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"array-data-structures","maybeAbsoluteLinks":[]},"frontmatter":{"title":"Array Data Structures in Python"}},"translations":[],"translatedLinks":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}